### 1 - touch .eslintrc.json  
### 2 - npm install prettier eslint-config-prettier eslint-plugin-prettier -D
###Inside .eslintrc.json
>{
  "extends": [
    "react-app",
    "plugin:prettier/recommended",
    "prettier/flowtype",
    "prettier/react",
    "prettier/standard"
  ],
  "rules": {
    "no-console": "warn"
  }
}  
>

###3 - Add File Watcher : Prettier (js, css) 
###at the end of package.json  
>"prettier": {
    "singleQuote": true
  }
>
###4 - npm install --D husky lint-staged pretty-quick  
###at the end of package.json  
>"husky": {
  "hooks": {
    "pre-commit": "pretty-quick --staged"
  }
}
>
